Privacy Policy
Device Support Information is a simple utility extension for managed ChromeOS devices.
This extension does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. It only displays device information (Serial Number, Asset ID, IP Address, etc.) locally using official Chrome Enterprise APIs.

No data is sent to external servers.
No analytics, tracking, or third-party services are used.
The extension works completely offline.

All information is shown only inside the extension popup for support purposes.
